This product includes software developed by the OpenQuant contributors.

This product imports concepts and formulas from third-party publicly-available
research:
  - WorldQuant "101 Formulaic Alphas" (Z. Kakushadze, arXiv:1601.00991)
  - 国泰君安证券《短周期价量特征 Alpha 因子》报告 (Alpha191)
  - Barra "China Equity Model" 风格因子框架
  - TradingAgents architecture inspiration (Tauric Research, arXiv:2412.20138)

All formula implementations are independent ports based on the published
formulas; the source code is original work covered by this project's license.
